- **Project:** RS Recruitment – MVP
- **Stack:** Python 3.12+, FastAPI, SQLModel (Async), Alembic
- **Database:** PostgreSQL (Prod) / SQLite (Dev & Tests)
- **Environment:** WSL (Ubuntu)
- **Architecture:** Modular Monolith, Vertical Slices
